    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Google + vs FaceBook 功能大比較]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.sammylin.tw/google-vs-facebook-function-of-comparative/"/>
    <updated>2011-06-30T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.sammylin.tw/google-vs-facebook-function-of-comparative</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image80.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb79.png" width="270" height="163" /></a></p>  <p>昨天Google推出了Google+的服務之後，許多人都在要邀請的帳號，但沒想到今天早上突然筆者就收到一封信說我被邀請了，我也去湊個熱鬧來玩玩看，到底FaceBook跟Google+有什麼差別別，筆者在這邊來做個比較。</p><!--more--><table border="2" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">&nbsp;</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image81.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb80.png" width="129" height="46" /></a></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image82.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb81.png" width="153" height="47" /></a></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">介面</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">         <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image83.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb82.png" width="204" height="123" /></a></p>          <p>簡潔有力~沒有任何廣告<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></p>       </td>        <td valign="top" width="180">         <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image84.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb83.png" width="204" height="125" /></a></p>          <p>功能豐富卻有時會出現廣告</p>       </td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">活動功能</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">有<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">訊息</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image85.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb84.png" width="204" height="121" /></a>          <br />有新的訊息會自動的更新<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image86.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb85.png" width="204" height="111" /></a>          <br />有新的訊息只會在選單上通知</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">訊息貼上網址</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image87.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb86.png" width="204" height="126" /></a>          <br />兩者都可以自動抓取摘要及圖片</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image88.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb87.png" width="204" height="140" /></a>          <br />也可以選自已要的圖片</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">分享訊息隱私</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image89.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb88.png" width="204" height="94" /></a>          <br />可以對某個Circle分享訊息<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image90.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb89.png" width="204" height="95" /></a>只能指定某個人或是朋友</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">加入好友</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image91.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb90.png" width="204" height="70" /></a>          <br />在朋友的訊息中，將滑鼠移到你要家的朋友在按下「加入社交圈」就可以加入了<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">必需進到個人資料才能夠的加入好友！</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">延伸社交圈</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image92.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb91.png" width="204" height="86" /></a>          <br />朋友的朋友都可以看的到你分享的訊息！<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無，只能靠分享或是有朋友留言才看的到。</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">關連性</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image93.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb92.png" width="204" height="123" /></a>          <br />有結合Google大部的的功能，都可以有通知Google+的的服務<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">只有在FaceBook的網站上才能接收到通知！</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">直覺</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image94.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb93.png" width="204" height="128" /></a>          <br />可以直接在通知上回覆留言或加入社交圈<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無，只能裝外掛。</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">話題</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image95.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb94.png" width="204" height="120" /></a>          <br />可以加入你想有興趣的話題<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無，只能看到一些垃圾訊息</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">上傳圖片</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image96.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb95.png" width="204" height="95" /></a>          <br />可直覺用拖曳圖片至訊息框上傳圖片或影片、連結。(只支援chrome)<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無</td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">社團</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">有粉絲專頁、社團<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">票選</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image97.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb96.png" width="204" height="86" /></a><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">覺得不錯的留言</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image98.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb97.png" width="40" height="24" /></a></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image99.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb98.png" width="56" height="34" /></a></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">遊戲</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">無</td>        <td valign="top" width="180">太多了<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">聊天室</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image100.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb99.png" width="235" height="193" /></a>          <br />有視訊、語音通話<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image101.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb100.png" width="204" height="217" /></a></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">指定某人</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image102.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb101.png" width="204" height="105" /></a>          <br />出現了一堆不是好友</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image103.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb102.png" width="204" height="108" /></a>          <br />都是好友或是專頁<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>     </tr>      <tr>       <td valign="top" width="180">線上視訊</td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image104.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb103.png" width="204" height="65" /></a>          <br />可多人視訊<span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small">(勝)</span></td>        <td valign="top" width="180"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/image46.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/image_thumb47.png" width="204" height="176" /></a>          <br />只能一對一(2011/7/7新增)</td>     </tr>   </tbody></table>  <p>&#160;</p>  <p>看起來Google+感覺大勝許多，不過我有點以我個人主觀意識啦，<span style="text-decoration: line-through">有點在抱Google的大腿</span>~，然後我的手機太爛了沒辦法測試到手機的部份，希望大家可以做個參考，有空在做一個Google+的詳細介紹！</p></p>

